                    "body": "Thanks for quick reply.\u00a0\r\n\r\nI also found pypi and R repo didn't contain a pyarrow package, as it can not build/search the arrow package when I testing the associated test with arrow. So our community haven't release the ARM release for these situation right now? ;)\r\n\r\nTravis ARM CI is in alpha testing release now. So I guess it is hard for fitting current requests for now. But I think that will become more stable and powerful in the future.",
